  <h3>10. Weekly Backlink Maintenance Checklist</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>☐ Check Ahrefs or GSC for new backlinks – thank or share on social media.</li>
    <li>☐ Check for lost backlinks – if a good link was removed, contact the site owner.</li>
    <li>☐ Spend 1 hour on link prospecting (find 5‑10 potential sites).</li>
    <li>☐ Send 5 outreach emails (guest post pitches, broken link replacement suggestions).</li>
    <li>☐ Monitor your anchor text distribution – adjust if over‑optimized.</li>
    <li>☐ Ensure your best content has internal links from other pages (helps distribute backlink equity). <a href="/fix-internal-links">Internal linking audit →</a></li>
